*Bez* čekanja, dobio je odgovor. (Without waiting, he got an answer.)

On je *bez* nade otišao. (He left without hope.)

Ona je *bez* zraka. (She is breathless.)

*Bez* pravog razloga, otišao je. (Without a real reason, he left.)

On je *bez* imalo sumnje pobedio. (He won without any doubt.)

*Bez* oklevanja, uspeo je da ostvari svoj cilj. (Without hesitation, he succeeded to achieve his goal.)